&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/EUR-SWITZERLAND-SCHLOSS-SCHAUENSTEIN-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4338&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/EUR-SWITZERLAND-SCHLOSS-SCHAUENSTEIN-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;EUR- SWITZERLAND- SCHLOSS SCHAUENSTEIN- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-14488&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;50Best_2015_logo&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;88&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.elitetraveler.com/finest-dining/top-100-restaurants-in-the-world/schloss-schauenstein&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-3918&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-ELITE-TRAVELER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- ELITE TRAVELER LOGO1&quot; width=&quot;80&quot; height=&quot;80&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Schauenstein Schloss Restaurant Hotel &nbsp;is set in an enchanting castle that houses both restaurant and hotel. Andreas Caminada&rsquo;s creativity and technique has earned &lt;strong&gt;the&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#47 spot in 2016 World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants,&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#48 spot in the&nbsp;2015&nbsp;World 50 Best Restaurants&lt;/strong&gt;,&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;3 Michelin Stars&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;19 Gault&amp;amp;Millau points&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;The Elite 100 #79&lt;/strong&gt;. The dining room is romantic and elegantly cozy. A stay at the castle provides the opportunity to try a sumptuous breakfast by Chef Caminada. Attire is chic casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Schauenstein Schloss Restaurant Hotel by phone at +41 81 632 10 80 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:kontakt@schauenstein.ch&quot;&gt;kontakt@schauenstein.ch&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, lunch or dinner reservation, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant Schauenstein Schloss requires a credit card to hold your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy- Reservations must be cancelled 48 hours in advance or a fee of CHF 200 (including VAT) per person will be charged to your credit card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please provide a cell phone number or local contact number. The restaurant will call you one week prior to the dining date to reconfirm and discuss any allergies or special needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

